In the INTEREST OF: T.D.N.T.R., a Minor Appeal of: T.D.N.T.R., Child Petition of: E.B., Father In the Interest of: L.M.R., a Minor Appeal of: L.M.R., Child Petition of: E.B., Father No. 33 EAL 2019
No. 34 EAL 2019 Supreme Court of Pennsylvania. April 5, 2019

ORDER

PER CURIAM .

AND NOW, this 5th day of April, 2019, the Petition for Allowance of Appeal is DENIED. The Joint Applications for Relief by Participants Department of Human Services and Minor Children, T.D.N.T.R. & L.M.R. are DENIED AS MOOT.
